channel.title: AmbrosotoX! 667/711 24/7
channel.description:
This is a brand new server. We aren't running off of VPS so we are still in a somewhat beta stage. But we are running 24/7, and if you find a glitch or bug, just let us know and we will have it fixed very quickly. The xp rates are great, their enough to challenge you but not to high that would make it very easy. Everything is easy to find and get to.
If you wanna know more then try it out for yourself. Anyone asks, tell em Dylan sent ya.
www.ambrosotox.webs.com
